                        Shoot: The Shootorial Game

Shootorial
----------
This package contains the full ActionScript 2.0 source and assets for the
ActionScript 2.0 version of Shoot: The Shootorial Game [1].

The Shootorials [2] are a set of Flash game programming tutorials designed to
walk a beginner through the process of making a simple side scrolling shooter
game. The source code for each Shootorial is available via a download link on
the web page containing the Shootorial. Aspiring game developers interested in
learning the basics can use that source code as a spring board for making
Flash games using ActionScript 2.0. 

Shoot: The Shootorial Game is an example of the type of game you can build
after completing the Shootorials. 

Downloading
-----------
This package can be downloaded from http://www.kongregate.com/labs.

